[Civil. No. 546.] JAMES L. UTTER et al., as Executors of the Last Will and Testament of Elizabeth B. Voorhis, Deceased, Plaintiffs, v. BENJAMIN J. FRANKLIN, et al., Loan Commissioners of the Territory of Arizona, Defendants. ORIGINAL APPLICATION for Writ of Mandamus. Barnes & Martin, Attorneys for Plaintiffs. Rochester Ford, and C. F. Ainsworth, Attorney-General, for Defendants.' October 31, 1902.

Writ granted.
